Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要好好遵守那个约定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间已到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我宣布 月飨祭正式开幕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是我 我们店真是气派
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们相比 请看一下幸平的店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种小吃摊还想向我们挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我战胜中华研的第一招
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡椒饼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
